# Sound Effects Directory

Place sound effects here:
- laser_shoot.mp3 - Laser weapon firing
- missile_shoot.mp3 - Missile weapon firing
- enemy_explosion.mp3 - Enemy destruction
- projectile_hit.mp3 - Projectile impact
- player_hit.mp3 - Player taking damage
- engine_boost.mp3 - Ship acceleration
- level_up.mp3 - Level up achievement
- enemy_spawn.mp3 - Enemy appearance
- pickup_xp.mp3 - XP collection

## Recommended Specifications:
- Format: MP3 or OGG
- Quality: 96-128 kbps
- Length: 0.1-2 seconds for most effects
- Volume: Normalized, punchy and clear